tscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>4. </span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>实例化成统一的</span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>react event</span></p><p><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>5. </span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>通过</span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>dispatch event</span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>对应到事件处理函数</span></p></body>
