<node ID="810C8603-8DAA-402A-8691-453F7BDEE10E" TEXT="&#32452;&#20214;&#28210;&#26579;&#36807;&#31243;" COLOR="#F3F3F3" POSITION="left" STYLE="fork"><edge COLOR="#AF4FC8" WIDTH="4" /><font NAME="PingFangSC-Regular" SIZE="20" /><richcontent TYPE="NOTE"><html><head></head>
<body><p style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>初次渲染过程</p><p><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>1. </span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>解析模板为</span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>render</span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>函数</span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>(</span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>或在开发环境已经完成，vue-loader</span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>)</span></p><p><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>2. </span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>触发响应式，监听</span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>data</span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>属性</span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>getter setter</span></p><p><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>3. </span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>执行</span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>render</span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>函数，生成</span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>vnode</span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>，</span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>patch</span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>(elm, node)</span></p><p></p><p style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>更新过程</p><p><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>1. </span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>修改</span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>data</span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>，触发</span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>setter(</span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>此前已经在</span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>getter</span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>中监听</span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>)</span></p><p><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>2. </span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>重新执行</span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>render</span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>函数，成成newVnode</span></p><p style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>3. patch(node, newVode)</p><p></p><p style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>异步渲染</p><p style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>1. 回顾$nextTick()</p><p style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>2. 汇总data的修改，一次性更改视图</p><p style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>3. 减少DOM操作次数，提高性能</p><p></p><p style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>总结</p><p style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>1. 渲染和响应式的关系</p><p style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>2. 渲染和模板编译的关系</p><p style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>3. 渲染和VDOM的关系 </p></body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
<node ID="399FF017-9ADA-4C23-AEAA-0DCEAE78C5F3" TEXT="&#21069;&#31471;&#36335;&#30001;" COLOR="#F3F3F3" POSITION="left" STYLE="fork"><edge COLOR="#AF4FC8" WIDTH="4" /><font NAME="PingFangSC-Regular" SIZE="20" /><node ID="B934E17B-9425-4120-91E4-E1A875090742" TEXT="hash&#36335;&#30001;" COLOR="#F3F3F3" POSITION="left" STYLE="fork"><edge COLOR="#AF4FC8" WIDTH="3" /><font NAME="PingFangSC-Regular" SIZE="20" /><richcontent TYPE="NOTE"><html><head></head>
<body><p style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>location.hash</p><p></p><p><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>1. hash</span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>变化会触发网页跳转，即浏览器的前进、后退</span></p><p style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>2. hash变化不会刷新页面，SPA必需的特点</p><p style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>3. hash永远不会提交到server端(前端自生自灭)</p></body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
<node ID="9471FA6D-2AF8-46B3-920F-36E5E63EB094" TEXT="H5 history&#36335;&#30001;" COLOR="#F3F3F3" POSITION="left" STYLE="fork"><edge COLOR="#AF4FC8" WIDTH="3" /><font NAME="PingFangSC-Regular" SIZE="20" /><richcontent TYPE="NOTE"><html><head></head>
<body><p><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>1. </span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>用</span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>url</span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>规范的路由，但跳转时不刷新页面</span></p><p style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>2. history.pushState</p><p style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>3. window.onpopstate</p><p></p><p style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>Const state = {name:page1}</p><p style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>history.pushState(state, ‘’, ‘page1’)</p><p></p><p style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>window.onpopstate = (event) =&gt; {</p><p style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>  Event.state</p><p style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>  location.pathname</p><p style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>}</p></body>
</html>
